      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 3974,
        "name": "伊迪娅",
        "desc": "<p>活动专属角色。她是一位纯水精灵，也是瓶之国「琉形蜃境」的管理人。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/31/88072335/8f84efbb97c6667cbf39cb960acb5db8_1155215707175901391.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4604,
        "name": "莉利丝",
        "desc": "<p><span>一家枫丹的孤儿院—水仙十字院的院长，后来成为水仙十字结社的成员，并在涨水期期间孤儿院被废弃后获得了「红皇后」的称号。</span></p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/06/157749474/b6d86ff8dfd84cf744e57a516b1a14c6_7619274014928247414.png",
